============= Passives ============
Damage Immunities: fire, poison
Condition Immunities: poisoned
Death Burst: When the mephit dies, it leaves behind a cloud of smoke that fills a 5-ft radius sphere centered on its space. The sphere is heavily obscured. Wind disperses the cloud, which otherwise lasts for 1 minute
Innate Spellcasting (1/day): The mephit can innately cast dancing lights, requiring no material components. Its innate spellcasting ability is Charisma
